OL,3,C'Awful' April: Which household bills
OL,4,Care set to rise and what support is
OL,5,Cthere?
OL,7,FEnergy bills are the only household
OL,8,Fbill that are expected to fall this
OL,9,FApril, reducing by 7% for most
OL,10,Fhouseholds.
OL,12,FEnergy regulator Ofgem's price cap
OL,13,Fwill drop from the current #1,758 to
OL,14,F#1,641 ` a reduction of #117 or around
OL,15,F#10 a month for the average household
OL,16,Fusing both electricity and gas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
