OL,3,C'Awful' April: Which household bills
OL,4,Care set to rise and what support is
OL,5,Cthere?
OL,7,FThe energy price cap is currently in
OL,8,Fplace until 30 June, raising concern
OL,9,Fthat energy bills could rise
OL,10,Fsignificantly from July as a result of
OL,11,Fthe Middle East conflict, with latest
OL,12,Fpredictions suggesting this could be
OL,13,Fby well over #300 a year.
OL,15,FGas prices have leapt at the fastest
OL,16,Fpace since the outbreak of war in
OL,17,FUkraine in 2022, after Iranian strikes
OL,18,Fled Qatar to halt production of
OL,19,Fliquified natural gas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
