OL,3,C'Awful' April: Which household bills
OL,4,Care set to rise and what support is
OL,5,Cthere?
OL,7,FWater bills
OL,9,FHousehold water bills across England
OL,10,Fand Wales are to rise by an average of
OL,11,F5.4%, equating to #33 a year for the
OL,12,Faverage household.
OL,14,FThere is significant regional
OL,15,Fvariation in bill increases, with
OL,16,FSevern Trent customers seeing a 10%
OL,17,Fincrease, Sutton
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/21
