OL,3,C'Awful' April: Which household bills
OL,4,Care set to rise and what support is
OL,5,Cthere?
OL,7,Fand East Surrey imposing an 11%
OL,8,Fincrease, Bristol Water a 12% rise and
OL,9,FAffinity Water (central region)
OL,10,Fcustomers warned they have a 13% jump
OL,11,Fcoming.
OL,13,FAround 2.5 million households are
OL,14,Feligible for social tariffs, with
OL,15,Fsavings of around 40%.
