OL,3,C'Awful' April: Which household bills
OL,4,Care set to rise and what support is
OL,5,Cthere?
OL,7,FTheir spokesperson James McCaffrey
OL,8,Fsaid: "One in four broadband customers
OL,9,Fare out of contract, paying up to #9
OL,10,Fper month more than those in contract.
OL,11,FIf you're out of contract, then you're
OL,12,Ffree to leave and find a better deal.
OL,13,FIf you want to stay with your current
OL,14,Fprovider, pick up your phone and
OL,15,Fhaggle for a new deal."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
