OL,3,C'Awful' April: Which household bills
OL,4,Care set to rise and what support is
OL,5,Cthere?
OL,7,FThe exact fee for your annual road tax
OL,8,Fwill be determined by the year your
OL,9,Fcar was first registered, the type of
OL,10,Ffuel it uses and its tailpipe
OL,11,Femissions.
OL,13,FDrivers whose vehicle was listed for
OL,14,Fover #40,000 when it was first sold,
OL,15,For #50,000 for an electric car, may
OL,16,Falso be liable for the "luxury car
OL,17,Ftax" fee.
OL,19,FElectric cars no longer qualify for
OL,20,Ffree road tax.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
