OL,3,C'Awful' April: Which household bills
OL,4,Care set to rise and what support is
OL,5,Cthere?
OL,7,FAir passenger duty
OL,9,FAir passenger duty (APD) will rise
OL,10,Ffrom #7 to #8 for a domestic UK flight
OL,11,Fin economy, from #13 to #15 for a
OL,12,Fshort-haul European economy flight and
OL,13,Ffrom #90 to #102 for an economy long-
OL,14,Fhaul seat.
OL,16,FAPD is a tax on airlines and aircraft
OL,17,Foperators, but it is understood that
OL,18,Fthe cost of this is ordinarily passed
OL,19,Fthrough to the consumer in prices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
