OL,3,C'Awful' April: Which household bills
OL,4,Care set to rise and what support is
OL,5,Cthere?
OL,7,FConcerns over cost of living pressures
OL,8,Fwere addressed by Prime Minister Sir
OL,9,FKeir Starmer last month when he
OL,10,Fannounced a #53 million plan of
OL,11,Fsupport, targeted at customers who are
OL,12,F"most exposed" to the consequences of
OL,13,Frising oil and gas prices. Oil costs
OL,14,Fsoared in response to the war in Iran,
OL,15,Fwhich began with joint Israeli-US
OL,16,Fstrikes on February 28.
OL,18,FHouseholds may be able to get help
OL,19,Fwith essential costs from their local
OL,20,Fcouncil, sometimes known as the
OL,21,F"household support fund".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
