PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775113301
OL,3,C'Awful' April: Which household bills
OL,4,Care set to rise and what support is
OL,5,Cthere?
OL,7,FFunding is aimed at anyone who's
OL,8,Fvulnerable or cannot pay for
OL,9,Fessentials, such as food, energy and
OL,10,Fwater bills, and essential items. You
OL,11,Fdo not have to be getting benefits to
OL,12,Fget help from your local council.
OL,14,FIndividuals can check with their local
OL,15,Fcouncil to find out what support is
OL,16,Favailable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
