OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775113301
OL,3,C'Awful' April: Which household bills
OL,4,Care set to rise and what support is
OL,5,Cthere?
OL,7,FThe Citizens Advice Bureau also offers
OL,8,Fhelp and advice to those struggling.
OL,9,FMoriarty said: "With key bills such as
OL,10,Fcouncil tax and water rising from
OL,11,FApril and global instability
OL,12,Fthreatening further price shocks,
OL,13,Fwe're concerned about those who have
OL,14,Fexhausted every option to keep pace.
OL,16,F"So far this year, we're helping
OL,17,Fsomeone every 30 seconds with crisis
OL,18,Fsupport ` that's food bank referrals
OL,19,Fand charitable grants. And average
OL,20,Fdebt owed is hitting record levels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
